MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2009-1553. State ex rel. Walker v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 08AP-606. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County.

*1417Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal, it is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
